{"tid":1267093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［1984？］多功能智慧燈柱試驗計劃","createTime":"2019-06-29T17:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T18:50:09.000Z","uid":138060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8dbb20123ec69a9cea69ed49216ae9928020f4","tid":1267093,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2323527/%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%8D%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2323527%2F%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2595%259F%25E7%2594%25A8&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=5978b7ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2323527/%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%8D%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n柱身中間可視乎使用功能，安裝最多3個「甜甜圈」形狀的圓型外殼，用作放置智能裝置，如<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攝影機、感應器</span></span>等。圓型外殼以玻璃纖維製作，除了保護裝置，亦不會干擾天綫訊號；外殼部分位置為透明，亦可以按裝置需要調節高度。此外，燈柱和圓型外殼的顏色能夠轉換，配合不同地區主題。<br />\n<br />\n多個政府部門會在燈柱上安裝裝置，例如燈柱上部的圓型外殼內有全景攝影機，供運輸署收集實時交通數據，及供環保署收集非法傾倒數據；運輸署會在頂部掛上熱能交通探測器及監察攝影機；地政總署亦會藉無綫射頻識別及燈柱地理位置二維碼，提供定位及周邊設施資訊。而燈柱頂部有預留位置供電訊商安裝4G或5G小型基站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c137fcc8003b2358d63cb1e79fb1c1a2dd5af65","tid":1267093,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"觀塘係咪落成左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56c5c3ba0e6ee7a53b19735fec9cb84a6c2299a","tid":1267093,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike"